<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Never-Type on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/never-type/</link><description>Recent content in Never-Type on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/never-type/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript TS2367 — Comparison Appears to Be Unintentional</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2367/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2367/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ts2367--this-comparison-appears-to-be-unintentional"&gt;TS2367 — This comparison appears to be unintentional&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TS2367 occurs when a comparison is always &lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; or always &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt; because the two sides of the comparison have types with no overlap. TypeScript flags these as likely bugs — you&amp;rsquo;re comparing values that can never be equal (or always are).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Comparing a type with a value it can never hold
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;active&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;inactive&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) { &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367: This comparison appears to be unintentional
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// &amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34; is not in the union
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Comparing a string literal union with an invalid value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;red&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;green&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;blue&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;isRed&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;color&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;yellow&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Comparing a number enum with a non-existent member
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Direction&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Up&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Down&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;isLeft&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Direction&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Up&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367: Comparison always false
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Comparing &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; type with anything
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exhaustive&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;something&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {} &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-valid-values-from-the-union"&gt;Fix 1: Use valid values from the union&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;active&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;inactive&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {} &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;active&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {} &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Valid comparison
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-widen-the-type-to-accept-the-comparison-value"&gt;Fix 2: Widen the type to accept the comparison value&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;active&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;inactive&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — if &amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34; is a valid state, add it to the union
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;active&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;inactive&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;status&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;deleted&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {} &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// OK
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-remove-impossible-branches"&gt;Fix 3: Remove impossible branches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Fruit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;banana&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fruit&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Fruit&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fruit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;orange&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This branch is unreachable — TS2367
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;This never happens&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fruit&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Just handle valid cases
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-a-type-guard-function-for-runtime-checks"&gt;Fix 4: Use a type guard function for runtime checks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;isString&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;unknown&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;string&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;isString&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;x&lt;/span&gt;)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// x is string here
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Exhaustive switch without proper typing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;area&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; Math.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;PI&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Comparing different enum types
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;A&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Y&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;B&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Y&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;eq&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;A&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;X&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;B&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2367: A.X and B.X are different types
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2367/"&gt;TS2366: A function whose declared type is neither &amp;lsquo;undefined&amp;rsquo; nor &amp;lsquo;void&amp;rsquo; must return a value&lt;/a&gt; — related to unreachable code.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts2345/"&gt;TS2345: Argument of type &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is not assignable&lt;/a&gt; — passing invalid values to functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/ts18046/"&gt;TS18046: &amp;lsquo;X&amp;rsquo; is of type &amp;lsquo;unknown&amp;rsquo;&lt;/a&gt; — untyped values need narrowing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] TypeScript Type 'never' Has No Properties — Exhaustive Check Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/never-type/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/typescript/never-type/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="typescript-type-never-has-no-properties"&gt;TypeScript: Type &amp;rsquo;never&amp;rsquo; has no properties&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; type represents values that never occur — a function that always throws, or a variable that can never be assigned a value. When you see &amp;ldquo;Type &amp;rsquo;never&amp;rsquo; has no properties&amp;rdquo;, you are trying to access properties or call methods on a value that TypeScript has determined is unreachable. This is actually a powerful feature for exhaustive type checking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Switch statement missing a case&lt;/strong&gt; — TypeScript narrows to &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; when all cases are covered, but if you add a new case, the &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; check catches it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dead code after return/throw&lt;/strong&gt; — code that TypeScript knows cannot execute&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incorrect type narrowing&lt;/strong&gt; — a condition that TypeScript determines is impossible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generic default resolving to never&lt;/strong&gt; — a type parameter that defaults to &lt;code&gt;never&lt;/code&gt; is used directly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Switch statement not exhaustive
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;area&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.14&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Missing &amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34; case — no error here but adding it later causes issues
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: use exhaustive check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;area&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.14&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;triangle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0.5&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_exhaustive&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// compile error if case is missing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_exhaustive&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Accessing property on narrowed never
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;string&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;typeof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;number&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This condition is impossible — value is &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; here
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;toUpperCase&lt;/span&gt;()); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; has no property &amp;#39;toUpperCase&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Return type is never
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;throwError&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Error(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;msg&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;throwError&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;oops&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// TS2339: &amp;#39;never&amp;#39; has no property &amp;#39;foo&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Exhaustive discriminated union check
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Circle&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;radius&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Square&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;side&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Circle&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Square&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Shape&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;kind&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;circle&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`Circle with radius &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;radius&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;square&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`Square with side &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;side&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;`&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_check&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;shape&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_check&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ensures all cases handled
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: never in conditional types
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;NonNullable&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;undefined&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;never&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;T&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;A&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;NonNullable&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// string
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Asserting never for impossible paths
